<item>Inform policy development and drive change by generating evidence on the impact of policies, interventions, and practices on population outcomes.</item>
<item>Participate in interdisciplinary research teams to ensure a holistic approach to addressing health disparities. Nurse leaders utilize data to identify health disparities and inform decision-making processes.</item>
<item>Collect, analyze, and disseminate data on health outcomes, social determinants of health, and health care disparities.</item>
<item>Use this information to identify priority areas, track progress, and develop evidence-based health interventions.</item></list></entry>
