<item>Build collaborative partnerships with health care providers, community organizations, and other concerned parties to identify barriers and develop strategies to improve access to care, resources, and health promotion initiatives.</item>
<item>Engage clients and communities in decision-making by ensuring community members are represented in designing, implementing, and evaluating health care services.</item>
